Symbol.Script_VL:
! ============================================================================== ! Woman Sitting ! ==============================================================================
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.`, DLEV3D_SIMPLE, `Простой`
values{2} "iClothesType" CLOTHTYPE_BUSINESS, `Деловая`, CLOTHTYPE_CASUAL, `Повседневная`
if gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=4 if gs_fill_pen=0 then parameters gs_fill_pen=91
if iClothesType = CLOTHTYPE_BUSINESS then parameters a = 0.501045 * ZZYZX / 1.35 parameters b = 0.745199 * ZZYZX / 1.35 hideparameter "matPants" lock "matPants" else parameters a = 0.497739 * ZZYZX / 1.35 parameters b = 0.729199 * ZZYZX / 1.35 hideparameter "matSkirt", "matBlazer", "matStockings" lock "matSkirt", "matBlazer", "matStockings" endif lock "a","b"
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2
! const values for parameter: iClothesType CLOTHTYPE_BUSINESS = 1 CLOTHTYPE_CASUAL = 2
dim stDetail[2] stDetail[1] = `Детальный` stDetail[2] = `Откл.`
Symbol.Comment: Сидящяя женщина в обычной или деловой одежде.
